[h2]WHAT DOES THE MOD DO?![/h2][list]
[*]Adds an absorption system to all armor:
- If you take damage, your armor does not get damaged if it has an absorption charge, In this case, this charge is used up (like a armor plate)!
- The amount of absorption charge depends on the type of armor (light, medium, heavy, etc.) and sandbox settings!
- You can still take damage if your total protection is not at 100%, but your armor will not get damaged if it has an absorption charge!
- You can recharge the absorption charge (small metal sheet for vests, kevlar strips for other armor)!
- Tooltip UI for clothes with absorb system!
[*]Most clothing can be repaired using the standard method!
[*]Armor can be repaired using recipes!
[/list]
[h2]!!! NOT COMPATIBLE WITH THE MOD: ZRE REPAIR ANY CLOTHES !!!
!!! THIS MOD ALREADY HAS THIS FUNCTIONALITY !!![/h2]

